{"tid":2180703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工會係時候比壓力黑心商人","createTime":"2020-08-30T05:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T11:13:02.000Z","uid":102378,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"04b1b92b436707910348efcd88bd9b71fa192022","tid":2180703,"uid":102378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T05:12:51.000Z","msg":"上年有咁多工會 唔罷工唔緊要<br />\n但而家希望出聲 <br />\n唔好等員工被自願參加驗DNA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n既然講到明係自願 <br />\n公司就唔撚應該要迫員工去驗<br />\n黎喇工會們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發聲喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次齊心就事成<br />\n搞大佢 唱衰大公司聲譽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n齊心就冇人怕d屎忽經理<br />\n揸住雞毛當令箭<br />\n好似百佳咁<br />\n我唔信誠哥有落Order迫員工驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大公司應該會為聲譽放棄d On9經理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec9e94253e5d6c6444338bbd02f871206b074bae","tid":2180703,"uid":102378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T05:19:45.000Z","msg":"工會們<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收左會費就幫手維護會員呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6025b0fff5cf197eb4302d4856395de2361010ff","tid":2180703,"uid":102378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T07:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97aeaf876aa7cc2736ba0493935f649f322012e2","tid":2180703,"uid":102378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T11:12:23.000Z","msg":"工會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fefb78dc70c2114a06bfcc2bcf88f4ee0dbf3f1b","tid":2180703,"uid":102378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T11:12:40.000Z"